{"tid":2434802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白粉報屈許智峯寫錯「荒謬」做「荒謬」 點知原來唔識中文","createTime":"2021-03-05T18:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T02:18:44.000Z","uid":63183,"like":121,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"4861a8d17c6f390c44d11a9704b480976f1bf426","tid":2434802,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T18:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/TED.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FTED.png%3Fw%3D1200%26ssl%3D1&h=cfb7a8cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四十七名民主派議員被濫捕，流亡英國嘅許智峯議員同悲，但未有懷憂喪志，仲喺社交網站撰文鼓勵香港人：「在哀傷中，警惕自己，不要被哀傷吞噬，不要接受殘酷和痛苦為日常，不要嘆息『自己不能改變什麼』，不要習慣黑白顛倒的世道，每天提自己，要在這荒繆、荒繆、荒繆的現實世界，努力生存下去。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，有人就咁喺賣過百份嘅報紙乘機落井下石，借住「有網民」話許智峯寫錯字。佢以為「荒繆」一定要寫做「荒謬」，仲嘲笑許智峯話「可能許身處英國太耐，中文已經漸漸退步，完全冇發現自己將荒謬寫作『荒繆』&hellip;&hellip;但許就好似仲未注意到自己寫錯字喎」。殊不知「荒繆」同「荒謬」兩字自古以來都係互通，係所謂「通假字」。筆者喺呢度略略說明下，費事呢啲垃圾文章教壞後人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D.png?resize=600%2C882&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%2590%258D.png%3Fresize%3D600%252C882%26ssl%3D1&h=939313aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n謬字可以搭做謬誤、謬論，有錯誤嘅意思，我哋寫荒謬呢個詞語，好多時都用呢個「謬」，但其實「繆」先係呢個字嘅本源。說文解字就寫得清楚：「謬，狂者之妄言也。古差繆多用從糸之字。」將個字源講得好清楚：再古代啲嘅時候，多數都係用繑絲邊（糸）嘅「繆」，慢慢文字演變先發展咗「謬」呢個字。<br />\n<br />\n「繆」呢個字本意就有纏繞、交織嘅意思。所謂未雨綢繆，就出自詩經＜鴟鴞＞，講雀仔未落雨就要織巢。「錯」字本身都有交織嘅意思，例如「交錯」、「錯雜」。又因為「錯繆」兩字可以經常同用，就喺先秦嘅時候，已經可以解作「錯誤」，例如《莊子&middot;盜跖》：「多辭繆說，不耕而食，不織而衣。」《禮記》：「差之毫釐，繆以千里。」<br />\n<br />\n正路嚟講，漢字或者任何語言都係越用越多字嘅，所以漸漸啲人就發明咗個「謬」字去分工，多數用「謬」去指言論上嘅錯誤，用「繆」去指交織嘅意思。但我哋唔能夠因為出現咗個「謬」字，就去老屈原本個「繆」字錯；或者厚古薄今，話舊嗰隻「繆」字係啱，新嗰隻一定係錯。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>所以見到陌生嘅寫法，唔好率言話人哋寫錯字。起碼查下字典，上網搜尋下，查下啲古籍，唔好妄下定論。就算好大機會係錯字，都唔好「執到寶」咁樣，因為錯字都唔係好大件事&mdash;&mdash;可以係手民之誤，可能係通假字，分分鐘原來錯嘅只係自己。</strong><br />\n<br />\n世態荒繆，但我哋唔好習慣黑白顛倒。「可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。」因為點扭屎忽花都好，<strong>蛆蟲都只會係蛆蟲，以為得主子畀啖好食，明眼人都會睇得出你只係食緊屎。</strong><br />\n<br />\n文／陳樂行<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5739&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=1ed0ee3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5739</a>"},{"pid":"d1405fa3cb00d1d3f7fad15421fcb7e8d154cede","tid":2434802,"uid":20641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T18:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de97e1e1f1eb0f5604dd6a233296cb1c6431f987","tid":2434802,"uid":35430,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T18:31:44.000Z","msg":"百份係咪又搵大陸仔做編輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d6693e777b23295e2f2dd934b693a61210f83d","tid":2434802,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T18:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5061a0cb99ac1969d833841a3048a542685c792","tid":2434802,"uid":146535,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T18:34:43.000Z","msg":"話人地喺英國<br />\n佢地身喺香港咪又係唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n刷鞋刷唔切"},{"pid":"c7e853850d5d8d28fc61b45ea1ac682810af4ef4","tid":2434802,"uid":119478,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T18:37:45.000Z","msg":"不學無術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d91fd2f97d503314ea064c4834d9de18fa5efc","tid":2434802,"uid":92435,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T22:47:25.000Z","msg":"好柒呀百粉仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當當中國人唔識寫中文"},{"pid":"8f6657b34606fd41d878b5b64a70a84b206bf16f","tid":2434802,"uid":283070,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T22:50:58.000Z","msg":"睇得白粉報嘅人會幾何多過書"},{"pid":"7457bd85c34f8b9aba5f704d1467a072b9c6016f","tid":2434802,"uid":52403,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"de97e1e1f1eb0f5604dd6a233296cb1c6431f987","tid":2434802,"uid":35430,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T18:31:44.000Z","msg":"百份係咪又搵大陸仔做編輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T22:54:44.000Z","msg":"大陸屄識字嘅咩？"},{"pid":"d697469fca7a874e2d6fdb7ff4f2f13c00a8210a","tid":2434802,"uid":305349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T22:58:09.000Z","msg":"又學到新野<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c516cd83b82f90f6126da6a77a41053590f4f39","tid":2434802,"uid":55583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T23:09:02.000Z","msg":"通商寛衣果陣又唔見你出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35572fdc1e2e123be7d420ee4a4814ff3c24f4e","tid":2434802,"uid":38793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T23:12:33.000Z","msg":"原來是世間太荒繆"},{"pid":"0554e37d83e09b80bba07982ff396a29f22810ff","tid":2434802,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T23:14:37.000Z","msg":"粉報未上電，係咁上下"},{"pid":"6c9ee85f1980e2bb41434b3d87182a9d7558fc6d","tid":2434802,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T23:24:23.000Z","msg":"馬爺冇咗個文膽咪咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12531e287d9a9ee31f01792eaf2b465daf9d1253","tid":2434802,"uid":271173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:03:14.000Z","msg":"同藍屍講學識、文采？<br />\n太高估佢哋呢班食緊屎嘅蛆蟲"},{"pid":"051f8a6ad6cae9fcb870be3f5fd2bdc5fe5cdce1","tid":2434802,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad53c19c54083378fab1eadcd2612f39861c7fd5","tid":2434802,"uid":32051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:08:24.000Z","msg":"配合國家發展正正經經賣白粉咪算<br />\n搞乜嘢報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5817eb76f3ceabebae8f219165530bc4a2f998","tid":2434802,"uid":166080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:18:01.000Z","msg":"藍屍支畜狗連中文都唔識"},{"pid":"5f4de0cf331a262ed39553f72da196ba19df3447","tid":2434802,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:20:50.000Z","msg":"白粉報寫文嗰班嘅水平同大公報差唔多啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c23c98ec775d1a307dc9b4bdddf0ce1ada14db1","tid":2434802,"uid":337444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:33:07.000Z","msg":"方丈垃圾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905a307833ac0207af09d2a5eff4409c22efd123","tid":2434802,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:52:16.000Z","msg":"西方日報"},{"pid":"3395b5366af59a8a6e29c33eb5b11bedd0671286","tid":2434802,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:54:52.000Z","msg":"海洛英 百份"},{"pid":"abb1ae080da1bcbf5d1e47bf64e5eb569542d560","tid":2434802,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:57:21.000Z","msg":"跳灰走去辦報，荼毒完人身到荼毒人心。"},{"pid":"0add9bccbadb2f945a566cb8f48fd147150636f0","tid":2434802,"uid":382841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:01:05.000Z","msg":"完美演繹香港人個種<br />\n急住捉人錯字捉讀音既心態<br />\n但今次捉錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33112d4c1b68d298a93064abcc91c79566b26a2b","tid":2434802,"uid":194130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:04:16.000Z","msg":"樓主都寫錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地果句本身係 寫錯「荒謬」做「荒<span class=\"red\">繆</span>」<br />\n樓主個標題變左2個字一樣 寫錯「荒謬」做「荒<span class=\"red\">謬</span>」<br />\n然後又因為2個字通用又變冇錯?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}